      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's way more than just a bad actor though. i've tried changing my passwords and checking my logins but everything looks totally normal. the weird part is that the posts are happening in real time. like if i'm thinking about something or just finished a conversation, a post goes up that's basically my exact vibe. sometimes i feel like the \"real\" me is being pushed out and the one online is the one that's actually alive now. do you think it could be some kind of automated system that's basically become my digital twin without me knowing?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
